-- JBS Holding Pulpmaking Unit Names ETH’s Grubisich as Chief
-- B y   T e l m a   M a r o t t o
-- 2012-01-28T16:10:04Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-28/jbs-holding-pulpmaking-unit-names-eth-s-grubisich-as-chief.html
Jose Carlos Grubisich will become
chief executive officer of Eldorado Celulose e Papel, the
pulpmaker controlled by J&F Participacoes SA, according to J&F’s
press department.  Grubisich had been chief executive of Brazilian ethanol
producer ETH Bioenergia SA.  J&F Participacoes also controls  JBS SA (JBSS3) , the world’s largest
beef producer.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Telma Marotto in  Sao Paulo  at 
 tmarotto1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Helder Marinho at 
 hmarinho@bloomberg.net . 